        "content": "<p>Hi, All, I wan't to build a minimal kernel for arm64, and build rust samples failed.  The following is my kernel configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">General</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setup</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Initial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">RAM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">filesystem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">RAM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">disk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">initramfs</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">initrd</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">hp</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">initramfs</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cpio</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">gz</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Initramfs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">General</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setup</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">General</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setup</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Configure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">standard</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">features</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">expert</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">users</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Enable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">printk</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Executable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">formats</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Emulations</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ELF</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">binaries</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">starting</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>#<span class=\"o\">!</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Drivers</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Generic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Driver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Options</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Maintain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devtmpfs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">filesystem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">Automount</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devtmpfs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">after</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mounted</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rootfs</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Drivers</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Character</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devices</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Enable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TTY</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Drivers</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Character</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">devices</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Serial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">drivers</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ARM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AMBA</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PL010</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">serial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">port</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">Support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">console</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">on</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AMBA</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">serial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">port</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ARM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AMBA</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PL011</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">serial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">port</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">Support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">console</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">on</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AMBA</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">serial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">port</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">File</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">systems</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Pseudo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">filesystems</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">proc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">system</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sysfs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">system</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Enable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">loadable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">support</span>\n\n-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Sample</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">code</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">samples</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">Hello_World</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I got an error when compiling the kernel module:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/3XWkPmraENFAprVAjsLFl2zz/ISQY7LEX27N4CALZ5T.png\">ISQY7LEX27N4CALZ5T.png</a><br>\nIn addition to <strong>Rust support</strong>, what other kernel configurations need to be turned on?</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/3XWkPmraENFAprVAjsLFl2zz/ISQY7LEX27N4CAL