    {
        "content": "<p>Regarding this problem, I have solved it:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">error</span>: <span class=\"nc\">target</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"./scripts/target.json\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">does</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exist</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>When compiling the arm64 module, need to add ARCH=arm64 to the Makefile.<br>\nlike this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">KDIR</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">?=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">~/</span><span class=\"n\">Linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_for_linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">next_0423</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">obj</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>:<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hello_world</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">all</span>:\n    <span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">MAKE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">KDIR</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">PWD</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ARCH</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">arm64</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">modules</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">clean</span>:\n    <span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">MAKE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">KDIR</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">PWD</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">clean</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 435007099,
        "sender_full_name": "Peng He",
        "timestamp": 1713885003
